<section>
  <h2 id="using-sublime-and-chrome">Using Sublime and Chrome?</h2>

  <p><strong>This may be helpful:</strong> &#8594;</p>

  <p><a href="http://sokolovstas.github.io/SublimeWebInspector/">Sublime Web Inspector</a></p>

  <ul>
    <li>auto reload on save</li>
    <li>console output goes to your text editor</li>
    <li>setup:
      <ul>
        <li>install via package manager</li>
        <li>restart chrome in debug mode - apple-shift-R in Sublime</li>
        <li>apple-shift-R in Sublime again to choose tab to debug</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>
